    "introduction": "Rural Finland in winter. An icy river emanating coldness and danger. A human-shaped figure lying still in the snow. A love story that pulls you under the surface. L/OVER is a crossbreed of drama and psychological thriller. It explores how and why coercive control can be the greatest danger in a relationship. What first seems like a love story of the century turns into something horrific. The twisted and distorted love story brings up a question – who will get out of this alive?",
